   <h2> ２００８年“中国１０大性 <a href="forum.php?mod=viewthread&amp;tid=40058&amp;page=1&amp;authorid=4079&amp;mobile=2" rel="nofollow" class="blue" style="font-size:12px;font-weight:normal;margin-left:10px;">只看楼主</a> </h2>
   <style type="text/css">.adlink{ padding:5px; line-height:24px; font-size:14px;}.adlink span,.adlink a{ float:left;}.adlink span{ margin-right:10px; padding:0 5px; background:#C00; color:#fff;-moz-border-radius:5px; -webkit-border-radius:5px; border-radius:5px;}.adimg{ padding:10px 0;}.adimg img{ width:100%;}.fixed_ad{ position:fixed; width:100%; height:auto; left:0px; top:0px; z-index:300;}.fixed_ad_content{ padding:10px;background:#000; background:rgba(0,0,0,0.6); filter:alpha(opacity=60); color:#fff;}.fixed_ad_content a{ color:#fff;}.fixed_ad_content span.close{ float:right; width:24px; height:24px; line-height:24px; text-align:center; font-size:18px;}</style> 
   <div class="plc cl" id="pid348523"> 
    <span class="avatar"><img src="http://www.bzbbs.com/uc_server/avatar.php?uid=4079&amp;size=small" style="width:32px;height:32px;" /></span> 
